             ViewProviderUpdatePassword, ViewProviderUpdatePreference,
             ViewPreferenceAction, ViewProviderPreferenceQuickLinks,
             ViewObarChecklistEdit, ViewObarRiskEdit, ViewStoreApptInSession)
             enforce POST-only in the Action class. -->
